Class ExcessReportPanel

java.lang.Object
ExcessReportPanel
public class ExcessReportPanel extends Object
Excess Report Panel
ExcessReportPanel is a JPanel that contains a UI for generating an Excess Report given a start date. The report contains all the items that have been less than 10% sold since the given start date.
